profile:
Wood Mechanical Heating and Cooling is a fully licensed and insured, family owned and operated business that has been serving the whole Essex County area for over 10 years.

Wood mechanical specializes in the installation, service and repair of all makes and models of heating and cooling systems.

We pride ourselves on providing top-notch expertise and service to both residential and commercial customers.
